{"tid":1729795,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone史上最大的資安漏洞！14款機型受災　3分鐘即可能被入侵","createTime":"2019-11-17T11:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T14:46:37.000Z","uid":32511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"62aeffb5d5b19599e7656080283267fc222cb9ff","tid":1729795,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:04:56.000Z","msg":"不久前，蘋果iPhone被發現根本性的硬體漏洞Checkm8，讓搭載A5至A11處理晶片的蘋果設備進行越獄，且蘋果無法透過更新軟體阻止，Checkm8也被稱為「iPhone 史上最大資安危機」。受影響的機型高達14款，甚至對方只要拿到你的手機，3分鐘就可以植入惡意軟體，或獲得部分的重要資料。<br />\n <br />\n而相關的機型民眾，專家提出4個建議，一，設備盡速升級；二，盡量別讓手機離開身邊，若離開身邊變成「重新開機後必須解鎖密碼」，請直接重新開機，手機可能已經被破解；三，確保App檔名不包含敏感資訊；四，連接充電器裝置時，謹慎按下「信任」按鈕。<br />\n <br />\n據悉，checkm8 屬於出現在無法更新的「硬體」上的漏洞，導致有這個漏洞的裝置無論如何系統更新都無法修正（bootrom exploit）。<br />\n <br />\n根據了解，Checkm8 影響的裝置範圍非常廣大，從iPhone 4s到iPhone X、iPhone 8接都被影響，當然，在這期間發佈的所有iPad、iPod touch、Apple TV、Apple Watch，甚至HomePod 也包括在內。<br />\n <br />\n唯一不受到影響的只有 iPhone XR、iPhone XS、iPhone 11、iPhone 11 Pro。因此也有專家呼籲，如果各界重要人士擁有相關的手機，應該立即更換手機。"},{"pid":"3a355e2650bccfbbc559e84edf58ed2abb124ca4","tid":1729795,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大獲"},{"pid":"3cf9f34e37fcb2c44dd341541e038691324232f2","tid":1729795,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:13:22.000Z","msg":"Iphone義士小心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"754dfdd0320a2e2918f26e60e061b1ec9f24c062","tid":1729795,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"咪用iphone <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27a825c71d5255c387a9d6f0c1526cec1e68c79","tid":1729795,"uid":214502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:19:33.000Z","msg":"想人買新機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d577b325b6aa3721e4264f5caef361da67fc62","tid":1729795,"uid":49151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"講咁多嘢最後都係叫你買新機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c856ab3eb65c155fefa36743459f757904d6746","tid":1729795,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:24:48.000Z","msg":"&bull;有能力嘅換xs以上機款<br />\n&bull;暫時換唔到機嘅，盡量keep住部機跟身，唔好比外人拎你部機，插線破解（咁都只會拎到一部分資料，要全破解，要解鎖部機先做到）<br />\n&bull;如果部機落低左，返到黎無啦啦發現要從新入密碼解鎖，代表有人撞過你部機，即時重新開機就得。"},{"pid":"ff2104186a940c96a975719f408346144907d780","tid":1729795,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:37:41.000Z","msg":"咁之前班狗話hack到入ios嘅原因係咪唔多唔少都關呢樣事<br />\n定純粹真係high tech問題所以比佢地hack到入去"},{"pid":"165d3ffb8457f3b3de104e3d22cc07a45e9059a5","tid":1729795,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:43:27.000Z","msg":"已經有得JB"},{"pid":"a358b5545e20bd3566c4dd6d90ed7b3d3f6f60b7","tid":1729795,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"假新聞 iphone唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2c772c2ec4f7ec6c9280fb5710a7bb2cfdeec4","tid":1729795,"uid":15909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a358b5545e20bd3566c4dd6d90ed7b3d3f6f60b7","tid":1729795,"uid":159448,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"假新聞 iphone唔會有事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T14:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5158055a9cc0e3e123b2d24442bc65b